  <brief_title>Modafinil in Treating Fatigue in Patients Receiving Chemotherapy for Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase III Randomized, Placebo-Controlled, Double-Blind Trial Of The Effect Of Modafinil On Fatigue In Cancer Patients Receiving Chemotherapy</official_title>
